              data-animation-duration="0"
              data-animation-direction=""
            >
              <h3 style="text-align: left">
                <span style="font-size: 2.5rem"
                  >I’ve wasted so much time being depressed, that I’m depressed
                  about wasting time.<br />
                </span>
              </h3>
              <p><br /></p>
              <p id="isPasted" style="font-size: 1.5rem">
                I can’t imagine how many days I have wasted to being sad and
                crying and not being able to accomplish the things I need to do.
                I have responsibilities I have deadlines and none of them seem
                to matter when I am in these dark episodes. How can you force
                yourself to do what needs to be done when you feel so hopeless
                and numb?
              </p>
              <p><br /><br /><br /></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </el-row>
      </div>

      <!-- 核心部件-->
      <div class="translate-container">
        <!-- <el-row :gutter="20"> -->
        <!--input 部分-->
        <!-- <el-col :span="12"> -->
        <div class="grid-content bg-light">
